{
  "stem": "1061.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then if they did ledgers, and they puncture these round holes, which made a bag of confetti.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Well of course, I was-- I was absolutely it with a capital I when I came back home.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I had these bags of this wonderful stuff.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And of course, I think I was injected with printer's ink because I'm a very-- I'm an avid reader, and I have always adored reading.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I think this is where it really came from.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I-- I really-- this is it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Absolutely.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[DRINKS] Grandmother's-- my grandmother herself, though she was very religious, was very well educated for a woman of her time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She spoke French fluently, and she came from a very fine family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And as-- she bore 13 children, nine of whom survived.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And unfortunately, after the war was over, we found out that nobody from that family in Poland survived.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I really adored those two aunts, my Aunt Regina, very much.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we used to visit, also, as a family-- the family on my father's side.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Except they lived in Sosnowiec, you see.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So-- but my father's brother lived in Radom.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And that was closer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And so we would visit with that family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they would come to us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But going to Sosnowiec was a little difficult and the other grandmother-- by the way, I never knew my grandfathers, not one and not the other.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But the other grandmother would come to stay with us for a-- for an extended visit.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And whatever, a few weeks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But we were very close knit family, all around, on both sides.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, not really.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not really.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My parents attended a synagogue, but it was sort of a progressive type of-- this was a small town, you see.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a progress of type of synagogue.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
